Garrett Souza updated his status.
Five weeks ago, one of my closest friends at MIT finished her finals and excitedly rushed home to her family in Iran.
Two weeks ago, we FaceTimed and talked about our winter breaks and plans for the coming semester. Through all that MIT has thrown at me, she has been there, accepting me unconditionally.

516241610.text:
Five weeks ago, one of my closest friends at MIT finished her finals and excitedly rushed home to her family in Iran.
Two weeks ago, we FaceTimed and talked about our winter breaks and plans for the coming semester. Through all that MIT has thrown at me, she has been there, accepting me unconditionally.
